OL,3,CStorm Goretti set to cause chaos
OL,4,Cacross the UK: What are your rights?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer, Jamel Smith
OL,8,FStorm Goretti has forced hundreds of
OL,9,Fschools across the UK to close this
OL,10,Fweek because of snow and ice, with
OL,11,Ftemperatures falling below freezing.
OL,13,FParents are now being left scrambling
OL,14,Fas more schools prepare to shut due to
OL,15,Fthe storm, which has brought amber
OL,16,F"danger to life" wind and snow
OL,17,Fwarnings across large parts of the UK.
OL,19,FWith disruption expected to worsen,
OL,20,Fmany families are now asking what this
OL,21,Fmeans for work, pay and childcare.
