OL,4,Cacross the UK: What are your rights?
OL,6,FSo what rights do parents have to paid
OL,7,Fleave if a school closes, and are they
OL,8,Fstill required to go to work? What
OL,9,Fabout employees who do not have
OL,10,Fchildren ? ITV News explains.
OL,12,FWhat should I expect from my child's
OL,13,Fschool if it closes?
OL,15,FThe Department for Education said
OL,16,Fschools that close due to severe
OL,17,Fweather should consider switching to
OL,18,Fremote learning until they can reopen.
