OL,4,Cacross the UK: What are your rights?
OL,6,FMost schools already have plans in
OL,7,Fplace for remote education, which may
OL,8,Finclude recorded lessons, live online
OL,9,Fsessions with a teacher, or work set
OL,10,Fthrough an online platform.
OL,12,FCan I take time off work if my child's
OL,13,Fschool is closed?
OL,15,FYes. Parents are legally entitled to
OL,16,Ftake time off work if their child's
OL,17,Fschool or nursery closes unexpectedly.
