OL,4,Cacross the UK: What are your rights?
OL,6,FUnder the Employment Rights Act 1996,
OL,7,Femployees have the right to take time
OL,8,Foff for emergencies involving
OL,9,Fdependants, known as dependant leave.
OL,11,FLara Kennedy, an employment lawyer at
OL,12,FLeigh Day, told ITV News that this
OL,13,Fright is not limited to parents caring
OL,14,Ffor children.
OL,16,F"We need to bear in mind that this can
OL,17,Fgo beyond children. It could be a
OL,18,Fspouse or someone else that we're
OL,19,Flooking after," she said.
