OL,4,Cacross the UK: What are your rights?
OL,6,FDependant leave is available to all
OL,7,Femployees, whether they work full-time
OL,8,For part-time.
OL,10,FIt covers sudden disruptions to
OL,11,Fchildcare, including schools or
OL,12,Fnurseries closing at short notice,
OL,13,Fsuch as during severe weather.
OL,15,FEmployees should inform their employer
OL,16,Fas soon as possible if they need to
OL,17,Ftake time off because their child's
OL,18,Fschool has closed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/28
