OL,3,CStorm Goretti set to cause chaos
OL,4,Cacross the UK: What are your rights?
OL,6,F"What's reasonable is not actually
OL,7,Fdefined. So it really depends on the
OL,8,Findividual circumstances that you're
OL,9,Fdealing with," Ms Kennedy said.
OL,11,FShe advised employees to keep their
OL,12,Femployer informed and to provide
OL,13,Fupdates as new information becomes
OL,14,Favailable from schools.
OL,16,F"The whole purpose of it (dependant
OL,17,Fleave) is to get alternative, say,
OL,18,Fchild care arrangements in place. Now
OL,19,Fthat can be very difficult to get if
OL,20,Fit's an emergency," she said.
