OL,4,Cacross the UK: What are your rights?
OL,6,F"So if the school were to be shut for
OL,7,Fa prolonged period, then it may well
OL,8,Fbe at that point that your employer is
OL,9,Fexpecting you to have maybe found some
OL,10,Falternative child care arrangements at
OL,11,Fthat point."
OL,13,FEmployees should not face disciplinary
OL,14,Faction or risk losing their jobs for
OL,15,Ftaking dependant leave.
OL,17,FIf your child is under 18, you may
OL,18,Falso be entitled to unpaid parental
OL,19,Fleave.
