OL,4,Cacross the UK: What are your rights?
OL,6,FTo qualify, you must have worked for
OL,7,Fyour employer for at least a year.
OL,9,FParents can take up to 18 weeks of
OL,10,Fparental leave per child before their
OL,11,F18th birthday, although employers can
OL,12,Flimit this to four weeks per year.
OL,14,FMy child's school is closed for a long
OL,15,Ftime, and I cannot find alternative
OL,16,Fcare - what should I do?
OL,18,FIf a school closure lasts for a
OL,19,Fprolonged period and you are unable to
OL,20,Farrange alternative childcare, your
OL,21,Foptions could become more limited.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/28
