OL,4,Cacross the UK: What are your rights?
OL,6,FMs Kennedy said employees should keep
OL,7,Ftheir employer informed and provide
OL,8,Fevidence of the closure where possible.
OL,10,F"If it were me and the school was
OL,11,Fcontacting me, I'd keep asking for
OL,12,Fanything confirming that in writing,
OL,13,Fso you can obviously give that
OL,14,Fevidence to your employer," she said.
OL,16,FDependant leave is designed to deal
OL,17,Fwith short-term emergencies and does
OL,18,Fnot usually cover extended periods
OL,19,Faway from work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/28
