OL,4,Cacross the UK: What are your rights?
OL,6,F"If you can't afford the alternative
OL,7,Fchild care and prolonged leave is
OL,8,Fneeded, unfortunately, I think you're
OL,9,Fin a situation where you have to rely
OL,10,Fupon your annual leave entitlements,"
OL,11,FMs Kennedy said.
OL,13,F"And if those have also expired, then
OL,14,Fyou'd have to request unpaid leave."
OL,16,FEmployees can also make a flexible
OL,17,Fworking request, such as asking to
OL,18,Fwork from home temporarily, but this
OL,19,Fdepends on how quickly an employer can
OL,20,Frespond and whether the role allows
OL,21,Ffor remote work.
