OL,4,Cacross the UK: What are your rights?
OL,6,FMs Kennedy added that those without
OL,7,Foffice-based jobs, such as people
OL,8,Fworking in retail or on building
OL,9,Fsites, are likely to be most affected
OL,10,Fby the disruption.
OL,12,FWill I be paid for dependant or
OL,13,Fparental leave?
OL,15,FDependant leave and parental leave are
OL,16,Fusually unpaid, unless your employment
OL,17,Fcontract or workplace policies say
OL,18,Fotherwise.
