OL,6,FMs Kennedy said this will depend on
OL,7,Fyour employer, your contract, and, in
OL,8,Fsome cases, past practices. If similar
OL,9,Fsituations have happened before, how
OL,10,Fyour employer responded previously may
OL,11,Fbe a useful guide.
OL,13,FShe said: "It may well be that this
OL,14,Fhas happened in a previous year that
OL,15,Fyou've worked, then you know usually
OL,16,Fhow your employer reacts to these
OL,17,Fsituations."
OL,19,FShe advised parents to speak to their
OL,20,Femployer as early as possible to
OL,21,Fdiscuss flexible options.
