OL,6,FThe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,7,Frecommends a minimum workplace
OL,8,Ftemperature of 16C for offices where
OL,9,Fwork is mainly desk-based. For jobs
OL,10,Finvolving physical effort, the
OL,11,Frecommended minimum temperature is 13C.
OL,13,FThese figures are guidance, not legal
OL,14,Flimits.
OL,16,FHowever, employment lawyer Ms Kennedy
OL,17,Fsaid employers still have legal duties
OL,18,Funder the Workplace (Health, Safety
OL,19,Fand Welfare) Regulations 1992 to
OL,20,Fmaintain a "reasonable" indoor
OL,21,Fenvironment.
