OL,6,FAcas (The Advisory, Conciliation and
OL,7,FArbitration Service) says employers
OL,8,Fshould take practical steps to protect
OL,9,Fstaff if conditions are cold.
OL,11,FThis can include allowing warmer
OL,12,Fclothing, providing extra breaks for
OL,13,Fhot drinks, or using additional
OL,14,Fheating such as portable heaters.
